@fileurl=http://localhost:8080/api/v1/files

### 创建文件夹 (基本)

POST {{fileurl}}/folder
Content-Type: application/json
X-User: test-user@example.com

{
  "name": "documents",
  "description": "Document folder for testing"
}

### 创建文件夹 (带路径)

POST {{fileurl}}/folder
Content-Type: application/json
X-User: test-user@example.com

{
  "name": "subfolder",
  "path": "documents",
  "description": "Subfolder under documents"
}

### 创建文件夹 (指定用户)

POST {{fileurl}}/folder
Content-Type: application/json
X-User: admin@example.com

{
  "name": "admin-docs",
  "user": "admin@example.com",
  "description": "Admin documents folder"
}

### 创建文件夹 (根级文件夹)

POST {{fileurl}}/folder
Content-Type: application/json
X-User: test-user@example.com

{
  "name": "root-folder",
  "description": "Root level folder"
}

### 创建文件夹 (错误 - 缺少名称)

POST {{fileurl}}/folder
Content-Type: application/json
X-User: test-user@example.com

{
  "description": "Missing name field"
}